            <entry>Frequent error in <ph keyref="nm-cc"/> log:
                <codeph>ControlCenter.GetRunningServices timedout waiting for reply</codeph></entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>CC-3036</entry>
            <entry>Cannot use <codeph>mariadb-model</codeph> by name in CLI commands</entry>
          </row>
