            <entry>CC-3072</entry>
            <entry>Internal MetricConsumer <codeph>maxClientWaitTime</codeph> and
                <codeph>perClientMaxBacklogSize</codeph> should have defaults changed</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>CC-3101</entry>
            <entry>During a WAN outage, concurrent map read and map write errors kills <ph
                keyref="nm-cc"/></entry>
          </row>
